pawn supported by all of White's pieces should easily decide the game.} Rfd8 (
19... Rcd8 20. Bc7 Bf6 21. Qc1 Rc8 22. d6 $18) 20. a4 b6 21. Qb3 Nf6 22. d6 Bf8
23. d7 Ra8 24. Bc7 Qb7 25. Bxd8 Rxd8 26. Ne5 Bh5 27. Rd2 Ne4 28. Qd5 1-0

