Rd1 $1 $14) 11. Qb3 a5 12. O-O $1 $146 (12. e5 Nd5 {Radjabov,T -Morozevich,A
Beijing 2012} (12... Be6 $1 {might be even more precise} 13. Qb2 axb4 14. Qxb4
Nd5 15. Nxd5 Bxd5 $15) 13. Nxd5 Be6 14. Qc3 Bxd5 15. a3 axb4 16. axb4 Rxa1+ 17.
Qxa1 Nd7 18. O-O f6 $1 $11) 12... axb4 13. Qxb4 Na6 14. Qb1 Nd7 15. Be3 e5 16.
d5 $5 $14) (8... Bg4 9. Be2 Nfd7 10. Rd1 $1 Bxf3 11. Bxf3 e5 12. dxe5 Bxe5 13.
Be3 Qe7 14. Qb3 Nb6 15. a4 {, with some pressure for White in Coelho-Valerga -
