operation in the Russian system where White gets three pieces for the queen.}
Bxb3 12. fxg7 Re8 (12... Kxg7 13. axb3 Nb4 14. Rc1 Qc8 $1 15. Be2 Qe6 16. O-O
Qxb3 17. Bd2 $1 (17. d5) 17... a5 18. Bd1 Qe6 19. Re1 Qd7 20. Ne4 $1 Nd3 21.
