unusual manouevre (Be2-Bd3), White obtains a very strong initiative.} h6 (13...
gxh4 14. Bxh7+ Kh8 15. Bg6 $16) 14. Bg6 Bg4 15. Nd2 e5 (15... gxh4 16. h3 $16)
