21. Qxe2 Bf7 22. Bxf7+ Rxf7 23. O-O (23. Bxg5 hxg5 24. O-O $13) 23... gxh4 24.
Nf3 $44 {Black will have a lot of headaches about his king safety. In general,
White's queen and knight are much more effective than Black's queen and bishop.
}) 9. Be2 $1 {This is a critical position for the line with 5.cd5. I believe
that h2-h3 is not obligatory and White should instead continue his development.
