The threat is Na5 and Black's defence is not that simple:} Be4 (12... Nd5 13.
Na5 $1) 13. Bf4 c5 (13... Nd5 14. Bd6 N7f6 15. Nfe5 Bxg2 16. Kxg2 Rfd8 17. Bc5
$1 $14) 14. Rfc1 (14. Bd6 $5 Bxd6 15. Nxd6 cxd4 16. Nxd4 Bxg2 17. Kxg2 Nc5 18.
