21. Rb7 $44 {Cramling,P -Zhukova,N Konya 2009}) ({I think the best way to meet
the immediate} 11... Ne4 {is} 12. Nfd2 $1 {Matlakov,M -Andriasian,Z
Magnitogorsk 2011} Nxd2 (12... Ndf6 13. f3 Nxd2 14. Nxd2 c5 15. Nc4 Qa6 16. e4
Bg6 17. Be3 $14) 13. Nxd2 c5 {Otherwise White follows up with e3-e4 and
Black's bishop is biting granite on g6.} (13... Bc2 14. Re1 Bg6 15. Nc4 Qc7 16.
e4 $14) 14. dxc5 (14. Nb3 $5 {is much stronger with the idea} cxd4 15. Nxd4 Bg6
16. Nf5 $1 $16 {, winning material.}) 14... Nxc5 15. e4 Bg6 16. Nc4 Qa6 17. Bf4
