Bxc5 19. Rxc5 $14) 18... a6 (18... e5 $1) 19. Nc5 $14 {We arrive at a typical
position with White's queenside pressure and almost no counterplay for Black.})
14. bxc3 Bc2 (14... c5 15. e4 Bg6 16. Rb1 Qc7 17. Nb3 b6 18. Bf4 $1) (14... Qa5
